---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import obsidianfrog from "@/assets/images/illustrations/ranaobsidian.png";
import ts from "@/assets/icons/typescript.svg";
import py from "@/assets/icons/python.svg";
import expo from "@/assets/icons/expo.svg";
import firebase from "@/assets/icons/firebase.svg";
import nextjs from "@/assets/icons/nextjs.svg";
import ps from "@/assets/icons/photoshop.svg";
import react from "@/assets/icons/react.svg";
import tablet from "@/assets/icons/tablet.svg";
import ae from "@/assets/icons/aftereffects.svg";
import tailwind from "@/assets/icons/tailwind.svg";
import pw from "@/assets/icons/playwright.svg";
import astro from "@/assets/icons/astro.svg";
import php from "@/assets/icons/php.svg";
import gleam from "@/assets/icons/lucy.svg";
import flutterflow from "@/assets/icons/flutterflow.jpeg";
import wordpress from "@/assets/icons/wordpress.svg";
import yo from "@/assets/images/yo3.webp";
---

<MainLayout title="Caracolaracol | Portfolio">
  <aside
    transition:name="side"
    class={`hidden transition-opacity opacity-50 hide_scrollbar laptop:block  w-[20rem] h-full max-h-[100vh] laptop:w-[26vw] desktop:w-[21rem] fixed top-0 left-0 z-30 `}
  >
  </aside>
  <main class="w-full font-tommyMedium">
    <div class="mb-8 pr-3 tablet:pr-0">
      <div class="bg-cerise mb-6 flex flex-col h-[7rem] justify-center px-8">
        <h1
          class="tablet:tracking-wide tablet:text-5xl laptop:text-5xl desktop:text-5xl laptop:tracking-normal cursor-default text-[2.4rem]"
        >
          Introduction
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="my-1">
        <p>
          Hi! I'm Agust√≠n Rojas aka Caracol aka Caracolaracol, thank you for
          vising my portfolio!, you've gained access a detailed archive of all
          of my works. Although you can encounter mostly with my software
          development projects and colaborations, there is also a significant
          amount of artwork here.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center my-4">
        <Image src={obsidianfrog} alt="frog obsidian" width={240} />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="my-8">
      <div class="bg-violet py-1 h-16 flex items-center">
        <h1
          class="tablet:tracking-wide tablet:text-5xl laptop:text-5xl desktop:text-5xl laptop:tracking-normal cursor-default text-[2.4rem] text-platinum"
        >
          About me
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div
          class="p-1 tablet:p-2 float-right min-w-[12em] tablet:min-w-[19em] w-[32vw] max-w-[28em]"
        >
          <Image class="rounded-md" src={yo} alt="yo" />
          <div
            class="flex flex-col tablet:block mt-2 my-4 bg-timberwolf/5 w-full px-2 rounded-sm"
          >
            <h2 class="font-chrono text-3xl">My links</h2>
            <a
              class="text-xl text-timberwolf hover:text-ocre transition-colors"
              href="https://github.com/Caracolaracol"
              target="_blank">Github</a
            >
            <a
              class="text-xl text-timberwolf hover:text-ocre transition-colors"
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/agustin-rojas-c4r4c01/"
              target="_blank">Linkedin</a
            >
            <a
              class="text-xl text-timberwolf hover:text-ocre transition-colors"
              href="https://www.instagram.com/caracolaracol/"
              target="_blank">Instagram</a
            >
            <a
              class="text-xl text-timberwolf hover:text-ocre transition-colors"
              href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1p8NlNx_SESv5QeNiyZMEQTllUpHzBwEa34wesV15dyI/edit?usp=sharing"
              target="_blank"
            >
              CV
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="my-2">
            I'm from Santiago, Chile. Here I work as a software engineer at <a
              href="https://www.tipddy.cl/"
              target="_blank">Tipddy</a
            >, an small tech company with an awesome team that makes awesome
            products and services.
          </p>

          <p class="my-2">
            I enjoy building things and creating art with different materials
            each time. That will mean that when I want to create something, I
            dont mind to spend a lot of time by learning the technique first and
            then making the thing. I like the idea of never acomodate with just
            one way of creating art, by changing the way every time I feel like
            I already learned the skill.
          </p>
          <p class="my-2">
            I'm also into Organic farming, in fact I'm a member of an urban
            garden organization where I cultivate organic food in my own garden
            plots. Additionally, the organization publishes a monthly magazine,
            and I contribute as photographer and writer.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="my-8 clear-end">
      <div class="bg-ocre my-2 h-16 flex items-center">
        <h1
          class="tablet:tracking-wide tablet:text-5xl laptop:text-5xl desktop:text-5xl laptop:tracking-normal cursor-default text-[2.4rem]"
        >
          My Stack
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="pb-2">
        This is the set of tools or technologies that I currently use or prefer
        when I build my projects.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="bg-timberwolf/10 p-2 rounded-md">
          <h2 class="font-chrono text-3xl">Programming languages</h2>
          <div
            class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 p-2 rounded-md w-full bg-timberwolf/10"
          >
            <Image
              src={ts}
              alt="typescript"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={py}
              alt="python"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={php}
              alt="php"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={gleam}
              alt="gleam"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-raisinblack/55 p-2 rounded-md">
          <h2 class="font-chrono text-3xl">Frameworks & Libraries</h2>
          <div
            class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 p-2 rounded-md w-full bg-timberwolf/10"
          >
            <Image
              src={react}
              alt="react"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={expo}
              alt="expo"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={nextjs}
              alt="nextjs"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={tailwind}
              alt="tailwind"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={pw}
              alt="pw"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={astro}
              alt="astro"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-darkpurple/55 p-2 rounded-md">
          <h3 class="font-chrono text-3xl">Other tools</h3>
          <div
            class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-2 p-2 rounded-md w-full bg-timberwolf/10"
          >
            <Image
              src={firebase}
              alt="firebase"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={tablet}
              alt="tablet"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={ps}
              alt="ps"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={ae}
              alt="ae"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={flutterflow}
              alt="flutterflow"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
            <Image
              src={wordpress}
              alt="wordpress"
              class="rounded-md w-12 tablet:w-16 laptop:w-16"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
